# @iocraft-versions: v0.7.18
# @description: Add strikethrough text decoration support
#
# Add TextDecoration::Strikethrough variant for crossed-out text styling.
# - Add Strikethrough to TextDecoration enum
# - Add strikethrough field to CanvasTextStyle
# - Implement CrossedOut ANSI rendering in canvas
# - Update Text component to handle strikethrough decoration
# - Update MixedText component for mixed strikethrough content
# - Add comprehensive tests for strikethrough functionality
#
